# Styling Conventions

## Tailwind First

Use Tailwind utility classes. Avoid inline styles except for dynamic computed values.

```typescript
// ✅ Tailwind classes
<div className="flex items-center gap-4 p-6 rounded-lg">

// ✅ Dynamic values only
<div style={{ left: `${position}%` }}>

// ❌ Avoid static inline styles
<div style={{ display: "flex", padding: "24px" }}>
```

## CSS Variables

Never hardcode hex colors. Use CSS custom properties from `globals.css`:

```typescript
// ✅ Use variables
className="text-[var(--text-primary)] bg-[var(--bg-card)]"
className="border-[var(--border)] hover:border-[var(--border-hover)]"

// ❌ Don't hardcode colors
className="text-[#1c1410] bg-[#ffffff]"
```

### Available Tokens

**Backgrounds**: `--bg-primary`, `--bg-secondary`, `--bg-card`, `--bg-dark`
**Text**: `--text-primary`, `--text-secondary`, `--text-muted`, `--text-inverse`
**Accent**: `--accent`, `--accent-hover`, `--accent-soft`, `--accent-glow`
**Colors**: `--copper`, `--copper-light`, `--gold`, `--green`, `--green-light`
**Borders**: `--border`, `--border-hover`
**Radius**: `--radius-sm`, `--radius-md`, `--radius-lg`, `--radius-xl`, `--radius-full`
**Shadows**: `--shadow-sm`, `--shadow-md`, `--shadow-lg`, `--shadow-glow`

## Responsive Design

Mobile-first with Tailwind breakpoints:

```typescript
// ✅ Mobile-first
<div className="text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl">
<div className="px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8">
```

## Typography

- `font-serif` for headings (DM Serif Display)
- Default sans for body text (DM Sans)

```typescript
<h1 className="font-serif text-3xl">Heading</h1>
<p className="text-base">Body text</p>
```

## Animations

Use existing animation classes. Add new keyframes to `globals.css` if needed.

```typescript
// Available classes
className="animate-fade-in-up"
className="animate-scale-in"
className="animate-slide-in-right"
className="animate-pulse-glow"
className="stagger-children"
```
